    <abstract id="aspace_a4d5562a52320000818fa4e8587672ac" label="Abstract">Peggy Hamilton Adams was a fashion designer, editor of the <title>Los Angeles Times</title> rotogravure fashion page (1921-34) and a host for local radio programs (1929-33) that dealt with fashion concerns of the modern woman. The collection consists of materials related to Hamilton's career as designer, fashion editor, and socialite.</abstract>
